dio is the voice of black sabbath a powerful but overlooked black sabbath album with the definitive vocals of ronnie james dio . a mercilessly heavy song selection boasting excellent production , something `` mob rules '' ca n't say , strong songwriting and some of the best musicians on the planet . from this springboard you can see where dio went with the release of his next solo albums . `` dehumanizer '' will stand the test of time as one of the three best sabbath albums ever alongside `` mob rules '' and `` heaven and hell .